'''Roukiata Ouedraogo''' (wavutse 1979) ni [[Burukina Faso|umwanditsi w'amakinamico ya Burkinabé]], umukinnyi wa filime akaba n'umunyarwenya  muri Burkinafaso.

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Yakuriye muri Fada N'Gourma, umukobwa w'umukozi wa Leta. Se yari yagiye mu ikinamico ryaho kandi yari inshuti na bagenzi be b'umupira w'amaguru hamwe n'umukinnyi uzwi cyane Sotigui Kouyaté.  . Se wabo ni umutware wa Mossi wa Soumiaga . Akiri muto, Ouedraogo yimukiye [[Wagadugu|Ouagadougou]] kugirango akomeze amashuri. <ref name="pitroipa">https://www.jeuneafrique.com/136480/societe/roukiata-ou-draogo-actrice-sinon-rien/</ref> Mu mashure yisumbuye, yinjiye mu mugwi w'amakinamico yaho hanyuma azenguruka igihugu. <ref name="Africultures">.http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=18429</ref> Kugira ngo abone amafaranga, yafunguye salon ntoya yo gutunganya imisatsi hafi y'urugo rwe maze ategura imyenda. Nyuma yo guhabwa impamyabumenyi ye, Ouedraogo yimukiye i [[Paris]] mu 2000, aho musaza we yari atuye. <ref name="pitroipa" /> Yari afite akazi kadasanzwe, kandi yirukanwe nk'umubitsi muri mini-market kubera ko yitiranyije amafaranga na CFA. <ref name="Pajon17">http://www.jeuneafrique.com/mag/465703/culture/humour-roukiata-ouedraogo-feminin-singulier/</ref>

Yakoze nk'umuhanzi wo kwisiga no kwerekana imideli imyaka myinshi. Mu 2007, Ouedraogo yahisemo kwibanda ku ikinamico maze yemerwa muri Cours Florent nyuma y’isuzuma. Mu rwego rwo gukora amasomo, yanditse kandi ayobora ikinamico ye ya mbere, ''Yennenga, icyamamare cya Mossé.'' Nyuma yo kwakirwa neza n'abamwigisha, ikinamico yabanje gukinirwa kuri teatre ya Comédie de la Passerelle mu 2008.  Ishingiye kuri imwe mu migani yashinze muri Burkinafaso, kandi Ouedraogo yakinnye nk'umwamikazi wo mu kinyejana cya 11. Ku bwe, kwandika ikinamico byamufashije guhangana n'agahinda ko kubura se na murumuna we. <ref name="lepoint">https://www.lepoint.fr/culture/ils-nous-font-rire-2-roukiata-ouedraogo-humoriste-et-chroniqueuse-16-08-2017-2150306_3.php</ref>

Muri Nzeri 2010, ikinamico ye yakorewe bwa mbere mu kigo ndangamuco cya Gambidi muri Ouagadougou, kandi cyerekanwe kuri televiziyo y'igihugu. Kubaho kwa nyirarume muri iki gitaramo byari ikimenyetso cyo kwemeza inzira yumwuga ishobora gucibwa intege numuntu ukomokamo nka Ouedraogo.  Ikinamico yongeye kugarurwa nka comedi yumuziki, hamwe nababyinnyi umunani nabacuranzi babiri. Muri Mata 2011, Ouedraogo yateguye ikinamico yo gutera inkunga ONG Fitima, ifasha abana bamugaye. Yakoranye mu gitaramo ''ingingo ya 13'' yitiriwe Itangazo ry’umuryango w’abibumbye ryita ku burenganzira bwa muntu, ryakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 mu bitaramo byaberaga mu mihanda mu Bufaransa.  Muri 2013, yakoze igitabo cyerekana ubuzima bw'umugore umwe yerekana ''Ouagadougou pressé'', ku ngingo yo kwimukira mu Bufaransa. 

Ouedraogo yatangiye gukina filime muri Nzeri 2013, muri filime ngufi ''Marie et les gargouilles'' .  Yagaragaye muri filime ''Samba''2014. <ref>https://lafrolesite.wordpress.com/2018/01/11/unjouruneactriceafrofrancaise-43-roukiata-ouedraogo/</ref> Muri uwo mwaka, Ouedraogo yegerejwe na Dani Kouyaté kugira ngo akine mu rukurikirane ''rw'inyandiko L'Amour en cage'' .  Muri 2015, yakinnye mu ikinamico ''Roukiata tombe le masque'', urwenya ku gukebwa kwe.  Yagaragaye mu gitaramo ''Le Parlement du rire'' kuri Canal + . Muri Mata 2017, Ouedraogo yatangiye kwandika inkingi kuri Inter Inter y'Ubufaransa.  Muri 2018, yakinnye muri ''Je demande la route'', yerekanwe muri Festival Off d'Avignon . <ref name="Avignon2018">http://www.rfi.fr/emission/20180711-roukiata-ouedraogo-avignon</ref>

Ouedraogo yashakanye na Stéphane Eliard, umuyobozi wa firime.  Avuga [[Igifaransa]] na Bambara . <ref>http://www.lesagentsassocies.com/artiste.cfm/698469-roukiata-ouedraogo.html</ref>

